import React, { Component } from 'react'; class DataDisplay extends Component { render() { const { currentData } = this.props; const { flightData } = currentData; if (!flightData) { return (
No Flight Data received
); } return (
>
Altitude GPS (ft) {`${Math.round(flightData.altitude*100000)/100000}º`}
Latitude {`${Math.round(flightData.latitude*100000)/100000}º`}
Longitude {`${Math.round(flightData.longitude*100000)/100000}º`}
Velocity (m/s) {`${Math.round(flightData.velocity*100000)/100000}º`}
Accuracy {`${Math.round(flightData.accuracy*100000)/100000}º`}
Bearing {`${Math.round(flightData.bearing*100000)/100000}º`}
Headwind (m/s) {Math.round(flightData.headwind*100)/100}
Air Temperature (°C) {`${Math.round(flightData.airTemp*100000)/100000}º`}
Pitch {`${Math.round(flightData.pitch*100000)/100000}º`}
Roll {`${Math.round(flightData.roll*100000)/100000}º`}
Yaw {`${Math.round(flightData.yaw*100000)/100000}º`}
TimeElapsed {currentData.timeElapsed}
Payload Prediction (ft) {Math.round(flightData.payloadPredictionDistance * 1000) / 1000 }
CDA Prediction(ft) {Math.round(flightData.CDAPredictionDistance * 1000) / 1000}
); } } export default DataDisplay;
